  "industry_note": "UNS G10180 / DIN 1.0453 / JIS S20C — plain low-carbon steel (C 0.15~0.20%). Cold drawn round bar: σy ≈ 370 MPa, UTS ≈ 440 MPa, HB ≈ 126, El ≈ 15%. Hot-rolled: σy ≈ 220 MPa / El ≈ 25%. Plain carbon → PH/Aging 불가 . 주요: 구조용 볼트, 기계 부품, 일반강 표준.",
